<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1298 gunēṁṭi [Ā]śvayuja bahaḷa
<lb n="2"/>tṛtīyyā budavāramunāṁḍu kaḷiṁgaparīkṣa patraśrīdharmmadasa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>jīyyana tanaku Abhiṣṭārtthasiddhigā śrīnarasiṁhanāthuni nagaranu gaṁ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ḍamāḍalu padi lekla mā 10 padmanidhi veṭi reṁḍu kuṁcālu prasadamu nelapa
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḍi Apālu 6 Ēṁḍādi jītamu Enimidi cinnālu Iṁtavaṭunnu vṛ
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ttigāṁ baḍasi kutari gōpaḷikiṁ beṭenu Ī gōpaḷi Iṁtavaṭunu
<lb n="7"/>bujiṁci Ēnāḷlaku Okanāṁḍu Addamuvaṭi mrugu veṭaṁga
<lb n="8" break="no"/>lāru Ī dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śatruṇapi kṛtō dharmaḥ <unclear>pa</unclear>la
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nīyō manīṣibhiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatrurēva hi śatrusyādharma<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śatru<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>na kasya
